Happy New Year! 🎆

Fun fact: I feel most at home at a library and have spent a LARGE part of my life in them. Being an only child that’s how I spent my time. I will always be a nerd at heart. Starting book club and staying consistent with it has been one of my favorite achievements of my life. It keeps me accountable with reading and love the community we’ve built. If you want that for your new year DM me to join! 🤓📚

📚✨ When I first started San Diego Book Club, little did I know that I would also be wearing the hat of an event planner. This recent event was an absolute blast! Thanks to the incredible collaboration with @alinasauza , we bounced ideas off each other and came up with a captivating gothic masquerade theme. Her creative genius breathed life into our vision, turning them into a mesmerizing reality. 

The atmosphere was simply electric, with everyone dressed up in their finest attire. 🎭 It was a joyous occasion where we delved into the thought-provoking pages of "Psycho-Cybernetics," a truly life-changing book that I wholeheartedly recommend to everyone. 🔮 In fact, I even incorporated some of the techniques from the book into the event itself! 

Allow me to extend my deepest gratitude to the phenomenal individuals who made this event possible. First and foremost, a huge shoutout to @iry_na_s for her support with the setup. Her dedication and hard work were instrumental in bringing everything together seamlessly. I am also immensely grateful to @robdrafke who truly is my rock and supports all my crazy ideas. Thank you @itsnikivan meditation coach for guiding the meditation and grounding us before our discussion. And let's not forget my cousin @setayeshfeizi , whose skills as a bartender were unparalleled. Together, we crafted our very own delectable witches' brew cocktail that left everyone enchanted. 🍹

Furthermore, a heartfelt thank you goes out to @vanguard.media for capturing the enchanting moments of the evening through his exceptional photography and videography skills. 📸🎥 

Last but certainly not least, I want to express immense appreciation to the members of our book club @sandiego_bookclub . Your unwavering support is what keeps the San Diego Book Club thriving and flourishing. 🌟📖

This past year with you has been the best year of my life. I thank God everyday that you exist. You make me the happiest girl in the world. I love you baby 🤍 Happy 1 year anniversary! 😍🙏🏼🤍✨ @robdrafke
Merry Christmas 🤍
